These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, frog, snake, chinchilla
1. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the snake and the owner of the chinchilla##2
2. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Pet   | cat | chinchilla | frog | snake |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, sudoku, magic-tricks, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Hobby   | sudoku | drawing | skydiving | magic-tricks |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
City: marseilles, berlin, prague, london
1. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
2. the person traveling to prague is between the person traveling to berlin and the person traveling to london##2
3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| City   | marseilles | london | prague | berlin |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, yellow, azure, orange
1. the person who likes azure is between the person who likes yellow and the person who likes white##2
2. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
3. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Color   | orange | yellow | azure | white |

