2. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in august##2
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |    2     |    3     |  4   |
| Birthday   | august | january | april | september |

