.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, lily, rose, azalea
1. the person who growspoppy is between the person who growsrose and the person who growslily##2
2. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
3. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Flower   | rose | poppy | lily | azalea |

 